  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Adorable Cyber Desktop Pet to Keep You Company Online!</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Freely move and resize your desktop pet to create your personalized companion.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Import local music and let your pet become your cyber DJ, playing your favorite tunes as it accompanies you.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feed your pet by dragging files onto it (permanently deletes them, even from the Recycle Bin). Great for removing stubborn viruses.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lightweight on memory — runs smoothly alongside games, websites, and more!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Left-click to move the pet, right-click to open the menu.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Adorable Cyber Desktop Pet to Keep You Company Online!</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Freely move and resize your desktop pet to create your personalized companion.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Import local music and let your pet become your cyber DJ, playing your favorite tunes as it accompanies you.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feed your pet by dragging files onto it (permanently deletes them, even from the Recycle Bin). Great for removing stubborn viruses.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lightweight on memory — runs smoothly alongside games, websites, and more!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Left-click to move the pet, right-click to open the menu.</p></li></ul>",
